    "abstract": "A set of requirements for active Operations, Administration, and Maintenance (OAM) for Service Function Chaining (SFC) in a network is presented in this document.  Based on these requirements, an encapsulation of active OAM messages in SFC and a mechanism to detect and localize defects are described. ",
